# PRD: DOSXM2 - 3 Homepage Implementations (Expanded & Mobile-Optimized)

> **Note for Claude Code:** This PRD contains specifications for building 3 distinct homepage variations for A/B testing and client presentation. 
> **CRITICAL REQUIREMENT:** While developing these 3 variations (e.g., on `/v1`, `/v2`, `/v3` routes), the main root `/` MUST maintain the current "Building/Under Construction" page. Do not overwrite the existing root index until explicitly instructed.
> **MOBILE-FIRST REQUIREMENT:** All "Wow Effects" must be implemented with mobile devices in mind. Avoid relying solely on `hover` or `mousemove` events. Use `IntersectionObserver` (scroll), device orientation (gyroscope), or touch gestures for mobile fallbacks.

## 1. Project Overview
- **Client:** DOSXM2 (Real Estate Agency in Madrid)
- **Core Concept:** "El Poder de Dos" (The Power of Two)
- **Core Message:** "Vendemos tu casa como si fuese la nuestra."
- **Goal:** Create 3 distinct visual/interactive implementations of the same core concept, each featuring a unique "wow effect" that works flawlessly on both desktop and mobile.

---

## 2. Implementation V1: "La Dualidad Cinematográfica"
*Focus: Premium, immersive, visual duality.*

### 2.1. Design System (V1)
- **Typography:** 
  - Primary (Headings): `Playfair Display` (Serif, elegant)
  - Secondary (Body/Data): `Space Grotesk` (Sans-serif, modern)
- **Color Palette:**
  - Backgrounds: Alternating `#0A0A0A` (Dark) and `#F5F5F0` (Off-white)
  - Text: `#FFFFFF` on dark, `#1A1A1A` on light
  - Accent: `#D4AF37` (Muted Gold)
- **Layout Structure:** 50/50 Split-screens dominating the layout (stacking vertically on mobile).

### 2.2. Section Specifications & Mobile-Optimized Wow Effects (V1)

#### 1. Hero Section
- **Layout:** 50/50 split. Left side dark, right side light. (Mobile: Top dark, bottom light).
- **Copy:** 
  - *Heading (Left/Top, Serif):* "Vendemos tu casa"
  - *Heading (Right/Bottom, Serif Italic):* "como si fuese la nuestra."
  - *Sub-heading (Spanning center, Sans):* "En un sector donde la mayoría trabaja solo, nosotros somos dos."
- **WOW EFFECT (The Scroll Reveal):** 
  - *Desktop:* As the user moves their mouse horizontally, the 50/50 split line follows the cursor.
  - *Mobile (Optimized):* The split line is controlled by the device's gyroscope (tilting the phone shifts the split left/right) OR by vertical scroll progress. As the user scrolls down slightly, the dark side expands to reveal an elegant interior video, then the light side expands to reveal a bright daylight video.

#### 2. "El Diferencial" (Why Us)
- **Layout:** Dark background. Two large, elegant portrait images of the founders, slightly offset vertically.
- **Copy:** 
  - *Heading:* "Dos visiones. Un objetivo."
  - *Body:* "No somos una franquicia. No somos un algoritmo. Somos dos expertos dedicados a maximizar el valor de tu propiedad en Madrid."
- **WOW EFFECT (Parallax Portraits):** As the user scrolls, the two portraits move at slightly different speeds (parallax), creating a sense of depth and elegance.

#### 3. Metrics Section
- **Layout:** 3-column grid on dark background (Vertical stack on mobile).
- **Interaction:** Numbers count up from 0 when scrolled into view.
- **Copy:** "45 Días Promedio", "100% Éxito", "5/5 Satisfacción".

#### 4. "Historias Vendidas" (Portfolio)
- **Layout:** Asymmetric grid of property cards (Single column on mobile).
- **Visuals:** Initial state is B&W static images.
- **WOW EFFECT (Cinematic Focus):** 
  - *Desktop:* On hover, the image expands with parallax and transitions to a full-color looping video.
  - *Mobile (Optimized):* Uses `IntersectionObserver`. As a property card reaches the center of the viewport (the "focus zone"), it automatically expands, transitions from B&W to color, and starts playing the video loop. As it scrolls out of the center, it reverts to B&W.
- **Copy (Card):** "El nuevo comienzo en Chamberí. Vendido en 18 días."

#### 5. Prueba Social (Testimonials)
- **Layout:** Light background. Large, elegant serif quotes centered on the screen.
- **Copy:** 
  - *Quote:* "Vendieron nuestro piso en 2 semanas por más de lo que esperábamos. El trato fue impecable."
  - *Author:* "María y Carlos, Retiro."
- **WOW EFFECT (Fade & Float):** Quotes fade in and float up gently as the user scrolls, creating a serene, premium reading experience.

#### 6. Valorador (Lead Capture)
- **Layout:** Split screen again. Left side dark with a subtle video loop, right side light with the form.
- **Copy:** 
  - *Heading:* "¿Cuánto vale tu historia?"
  - *Form:* "Dirección", "Metros cuadrados", "Habitaciones", "Tu nombre", "Tu teléfono".
- **Interaction:** Elegant, minimalist form fields with floating labels.

